Package: countr
Title: Count Values by Group
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicola", "Rammell", , "nicolarammell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package makes generating summary tables more effiecient!   
    It contains functions to help you save time in your exploratory data anaylsis.
    Presently, the package contains a function to count up missing values by group,
    outputting a summary tibble of missing value counts. 
